;The coding region corresponding to the BcsRQ tandem was cloned into the pET21b expression vector with a C-terminal hexahistidine Tag on BcsQ. The purified selenium derivated BcsRQ complex was treated with EDTA and incubated with AppCp and MgCl2 prior to crystallization.
